    "11": {
      "id": "11",
      "speaker": "Rikka",
      "text": "How do you drow do that - find pleasure in killing? I got a goblin myself, yesterday. Shot her through the throat.",
      "context": "CinematicNodeContext: She's closed off, crossing one arm over the other to hug herself, uncomfortable with what she did.",
